                        <h2>Azure Data Lake Storage<span>Azure Data Lake Storage</span></h2>
                        <h4>Massively scalable, secure data lake functionality built on Azure Blob Storage</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="home_site_trial_storage-blobs">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="home_site_pia_storage-data-lake-storage">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
                    </div>
